Interface Vector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CourierDeliveryJobVector

    public interface Vector
    Provides the interface for a "vector" that consists of two points - a point "start" and a point "finish". This interfaces allows access to these two points, as well as providing access to the distance between these two points (length of vector), and the distance between "finish" of one point, to the "start" of a second point.
    Author:
    Hayden Charles Smith, z3418003
    Last modified: 19th May 2013
